{"tid":17351,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以前鐘意既女仔識左男朋友","createTime":"2016-12-01T19:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T20:31:47.000Z","uid":40490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e7eae19c1e7868cfabed58da57d5fb3affec32","tid":17351,"uid":40490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:43:06.000Z","msg":"自從佢半年前某日唔理我開始就同自己講佢睇唔上我 叫自己盡早放棄比較好<br />\n重等我自己呃自己以為過左咁耐既時間 對佢真係唔會再無feel<br />\n到今日fb見到知道佢識到男朋友 啲心up又返返黎&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係又覺得又小小解脫既感覺 至少知道我同佢唔會再有可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗我今日之後應該可以真正放低呢個人去追過第二個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5f9972a634d65d4330d7f5a9596ea7ba19c2b6","tid":17351,"uid":6080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:45:01.000Z","msg":"巴打 世上囡囡何其多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0648fe47e5106cb25d5d731403a06cd2d409aa6","tid":17351,"uid":40490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:45:51.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"c7958fbd87c47322236758c7d5216b7cda8f0fcb","tid":17351,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T20:11:11.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05120ef70669372c5b30d4f7bad32a1fa5798df4","tid":17351,"uid":28741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T20:31:47.000Z","msg":"你呢刻只係唔甘心人地有拖拍<br />\n習慣就好"}]}